Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,▶Dialogue◀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你認識坐在那邊長椅上的男孩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  應該是實央吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小的時候他經常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,和他媽媽一起來買我們家的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小鈴呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒來  說是沒有要加班的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  繪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.02,Default,,0,900,0,,還沒開飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:20.56,Default,,900,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直坐在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,駿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,上去拿點菜…{上で野菜貰ってきてくれる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,給您  是阿姨給的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞  一直都麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小駿  嚐口這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.94,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,來份咖哩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.23,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,還有杯飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下  民宿的接待在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  好好  請先在這坐會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,誰點的生啤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小哥  點菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  等…你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是店裡多出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…肚子不餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈…是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了晚餐的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這個  是給我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？啊…沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？不用這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,下得真急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才實央來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,說是麵包的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是從他媽媽的花苗上分株而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,實央他的媽媽好像去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是母子兩人  一下子變成了孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子還是高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很孤獨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天和前天都吃的是咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,別的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這個！
Comment: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是沒錢的日子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們吃螃蟹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,螃蟹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,蟹肉棒飯飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,蟹棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃  再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  不夠還有喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我能坐在旁邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝…你送的花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我問你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直坐在這裡  在看些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一直一個人不會覺得寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是一直在盯著我嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真噁心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你這真讓人噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,橋本他啊  有時候是不是像個女生一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,難不成他是同性戀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喔啊  我坐他旁邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要被動手動腳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小鈴？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你又暈倒了來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,駿  發生了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也謝謝小鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是談戀愛的對象是同性嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麼值得大驚小怪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你在寫小說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…不過這不是我的原稿  是在審稿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  怎麼都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要和我道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,「真可憐」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都用這樣的眼神來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了家人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,悲不悲傷  寂不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事只有我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要隨意的安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的！
Comment: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我單純是很在意你  想和你搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這只不過是我的私心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼
Comment: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,毫無說服力的理由  和搭訕似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,900,0,,駿  晚餐要做…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,900,0,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,900,0,,哎呀哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,繪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,美少年又來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天來做些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,繪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,駿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字是叫駿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  馬字旁的駿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字  是實央
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.59,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,差不多該回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.59,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,果實的實  中央的央
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.18,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,好  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.85,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,要早點回去做飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.81,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,我要吃咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:21.64,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:28.36,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,咖哩  咖哩  咖哩  咖哩  咖哩  咖哩！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,駿  你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你  釣魚技術真差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  魚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒釣到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  駿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.58,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,一條都沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.71,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,閉…閉嘴吧你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤？你說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你也吃完再回家吧
Comment: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我開動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,實央很會做菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…因為我在家也幫忙做點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是這回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,給  實央
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這人倒一點也沒進步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那你別吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他啊  老是在擔心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,繪里  別說多餘的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是事實對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.79,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,「哎呀  他家住在哪？」{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  他倆吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.34,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,「有好好吃飯嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,實央喜歡吃咖哩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:31.92,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,「幾歲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.26,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,我才沒這樣呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  喜…歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.72,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,快住口啊
Comment: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,「好可愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,行了你閉嘴吃飯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明那麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.56,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,繪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.65,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,啊  鈴  我想吃炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.06,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.90,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,喂  你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.48,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,我沒在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.78,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:56.82,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,小鈴  這個馬鈴薯沙拉真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.07,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吃撐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,吃得好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,駿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天  就要搬去本島{註：故事舞台是宮古島，是沖繩的離島。}的福利院了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  啊  那聯絡方式…手機呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有手機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩子  孤身一人什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,駿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,到那之後  我會給你打電話的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我說老師  來幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,別叫我老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,現實就是這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,另一邊你們倆在共築愛巢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這麼恩愛  可真對不起枯木老師您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了  趕緊滾啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  新房客差不多該到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤？我沒聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因為阿姨說想再要個男生來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,駿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在睡覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,駿  最近還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,欸!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,新的房客是說…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你要在這住下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  我已經二十歲了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在店裡能幫忙做的事  已經問過繪理全記下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你也喜歡上我吧
Comment: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,駿  太好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,繪理！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼好的新郎{ts: 物件：契約などの対象としての動産および不動産。一般指房產。這裡用「男人」其實就可以，但是要暗示契約的話可以「新郎」。}一生難尋喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,胡…胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你笑什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你們都是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:36.98,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,恭喜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.00,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.78,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這些花…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是用你給的花苗種出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,長得和你一樣快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我長高了不少吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  你是開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡上男生是沒有好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我用了三年去考慮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你自以為是的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你既然知道那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,理由什麼都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,駿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,…有點餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,行了  去吃點什麼吧
Comment: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欸…等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,駿…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  實央
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒來得及說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我來看你們了  媽媽爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,近來還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,屋裡好涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  你還沒吃早餐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？有進展嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一…一點沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,呃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,加…加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來  拜託你帶的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,冷敷貼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…我忘記了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在要去打工了  回來的時候買
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.12,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,去打工嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.85,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,嗯  傍晚回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.72,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,來  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了  請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,燉肉塊{角煮  沖繩的其實是ラフテー}和炒麩{フーチャンプルー，用了這個部落客的：http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_8c76c20b01010k21.html}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小帥哥是島上長大的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是…的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:35.12,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,叫什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.14,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,我姓知花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.11,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:39.62,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,二十歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.89,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,好年輕！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.95,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,欸  那你有女朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.81,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,啊  臉紅了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.88,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,駿  該去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點累  先稍微睡會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那今天我能在這裡睡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤？不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太率性了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是什麼都沒想過啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這些  是你自己做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀  有幫到媽媽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  太厲害了！幫大忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝實央
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,沒睡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上我去你們那邊  有什麼想吃的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你真喜歡咖哩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和作家老師一起的生活如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,普普通通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  大師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊  和他好好相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,裝作很忙嗎？真俗套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候截稿？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,明天寄出去就趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那不算是趕上了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你真忙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,忙著接待客人之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…店裡？不算忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小帥哥{前}真有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  實央
Comment: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,剛炸好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來嚐嚐看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我來個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…你吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在家吃過了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴做的多拿滋真好吃哇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴她多可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一點也不像你那邊那位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你說是吧  駿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,脫稿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我去本島一趟
Comment: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？現在就去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,趕著寄航空件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那實央也一起去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？啊…可我還得看店
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,行啦  我們會替你搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你那是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我不太能應付視線接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,本島人又很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？你哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你接待客人的時候不是能好好交流嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊  我為了能好好交流很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真敬業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,用這勁頭找個女朋友不是更好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哈…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去機場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,您…您喜歡…男人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我對小孩子沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我…被男人告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可完全想不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:23:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以有很多問題想要請教…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.89,0:24:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,隨時歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.26,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只能給你果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.73,0:24:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在在哪裡  實央
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.96,0:24:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,駿  你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.00,0:24:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可能會覺得我像個傻瓜一樣興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.80,0:24:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得我什麼也沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.42,0:24:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我在與你分別之後  一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.03,0:24:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.37,0:24:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但你卻不是如此嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我回到那裡…給你添了麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.30,0:24:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,實央！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.46,0:25:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻坂的 LIVEHOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.26,0:25:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找你  你就待在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:21.50,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{前}橋本他啊  有時候是不是像個女生一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.50,0:25:23.43,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{前}啊  我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.43,0:25:25.49,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{前}難不成他是同性戀？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.49,0:25:26.71,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{前}大事不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.71,0:25:28.42,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{前}要被動手動腳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.13,0:26:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.38,0:26:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為你也會喜歡上我…{ts: 我喜歡你，所以你會跟著喜歡上我}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.48,0:26:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我喜歡上了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.30,0:26:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.47,0:26:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要的不是女朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.33,0:26:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,起來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.60,0:26:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.82,0:26:30.61,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,謝謝您的光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.61,0:26:35.35,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,早上 6~9 點可以在食堂享用早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.37,0:26:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快看  那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.42,0:26:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.06,0:26:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  什麼  前台？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.35,0:26:37.81,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,退房時間則是次日早上 10 點
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.81,0:26:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  眼神對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.61,0:26:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.87,0:26:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.87,0:26:42.96,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,這是房間鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.96,0:26:44.88,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,請乘那邊的電梯上樓
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.88,0:26:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.82,0:26:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.78,0:26:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  駿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.99,0:26:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.84,0:26:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,駿…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.17,0:27:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…你要回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.46,0:27:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你喜歡的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.25,0:27:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而是普通的女生  明明會更幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.77,0:27:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看著你  我就不由得這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.78,0:27:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.14,0:27:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你有和女生睡過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.05,0:27:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是…有過
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.97,0:27:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有過
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.43,0:27:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.72,0:27:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且可以
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.67,0:27:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我  倒還沒有和男人做過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.79,0:27:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,欸!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.13,0:28:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.31,0:28:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我又沒對人家表白過
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟和人家是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.12,0:28:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,與其說了被拒絕  還不如不說出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.99,0:28:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  不過
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.58,0:28:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但我當初卻開口和你打了招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.63,0:28:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得不能放著你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.78,0:28:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,駿！來做愛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.74,0:28:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.50,0:28:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經兩夜沒睡了…{二徹}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.40,0:28:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.75,0:28:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼唐突不行的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.33,0:28:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,努…努努力可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.32,0:28:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 駿  快起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.96,0:28:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,飯糰  多謝了 {我就不知道這飯糰是哪裡來的 原作我也沒看見 動畫裡之後手裡拿了一個來著 我姑且當作是在點菜吧}{ts: 說夢話吧}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.82,0:29:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.28,0:29:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼睡著了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.89,0:29:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.15,0:29:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,駿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.27,0:29:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,說是都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.10,0:29:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  挺漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.98,0:29:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.55,0:29:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們倆可是要結婚了的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.12,0:29:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.63,0:29:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.92,0:29:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,願意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.77,0:30:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,駿…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.45,0:30:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天來做…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.16,0:30:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不做
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.89,0:30:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.53,0:30:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.91,0:30:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,駿你難道不想做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.51,0:30:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.05,0:30:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.53,0:30:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.77,0:30:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快去打工吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.05,0:30:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.29,0:31:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.91,0:31:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦說嘛  駿
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.94,0:31:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,乖  快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.41,0:31:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我會去的  說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.81,0:31:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,駿
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.43,0:31:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.26,0:31:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.57,0:31:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.85,0:31:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.95,0:31:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,未婚妻才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.51,0:31:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,原未婚妻才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.25,0:31:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼知道我在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.42,0:31:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你是來幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.96,0:31:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你心知肚明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.19,0:31:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來帶你回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.78,0:31:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.31,0:31:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.55,0:32:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫櫻子  剛才承蒙關照
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.24,0:32:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我叫{姓}知花
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.78,0:32:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.10,0:32:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是駿的好朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.49,0:32:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.13,0:32:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.26,0:32:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.07,0:32:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.61,0:32:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  贈書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.03,0:32:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.20,0:32:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,做得怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.84,0:32:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.03,0:32:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你問哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.69,0:32:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…說你是我男朋友更好點？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.65,0:32:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.02,0:32:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.89,0:32:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,未婚妻是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.55,0:32:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,婚約早就破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.29,0:32:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,從那時起我也和家裡斷絕了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.94,0:32:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.30,0:32:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.55,0:32:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,家裡讓我回去露個臉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.10,0:33:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,說得簡單啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.29,0:33:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.51,0:33:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.35,0:33:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微耽誤你點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.22,0:33:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.79,0:33:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,駿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.37,0:33:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在忙工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.87,0:33:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.67,0:33:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.21,0:33:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那  你也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.56,0:33:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.44,0:33:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然你讓我帶你參觀下島上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.37,0:33:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這只有海和山哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.71,0:33:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去山上轉轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.86,0:33:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你討厭大海嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.51,0:33:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我就住在港口城市
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.31,0:33:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.32,0:33:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.93,0:33:49.62,Default,alpha,0,0,0,,你們兩個…{\alpha&HFF&\t(1620,1621,1,\alpha&H00&)}睡過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.75,0:33:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.31,0:34:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,駿他床上功夫很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.54,0:34:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有禮貌又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.35,0:34:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該早點和他做的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.24,0:34:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟他  還從來沒能如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.41,0:34:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.04,0:34:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.10,0:34:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是來和他復合的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.69,0:34:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能  才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.71,0:34:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼都沒聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.12,0:34:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他父親的身體情況不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.18,0:34:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,寄了信過來的  沒收到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.10,0:34:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是收到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.26,0:34:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？情況差到需要你親自來叫他回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.62,0:34:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,情況還不算十分危急…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.78,0:34:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒那麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.38,0:34:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但這樣下去  他會再也不會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.40,0:34:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你想要和他結婚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.62,0:35:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他說了可以
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.97,0:35:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你明明知道…他愛不了女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.78,0:35:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.81,0:35:29.15,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,我說  他也該累了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.15,0:35:30.19,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.88,0:35:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能用點正常的方式交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.53,0:35:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不和他告白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.32,0:35:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.17,0:35:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒準這次就成了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.99,0:35:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對成不了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.19,0:35:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,凡事無絕對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.34,0:36:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不說出口  就什麼都不會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.09,0:36:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你真沒骨氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.19,0:36:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.59,0:36:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,…又怎麼會懂
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.41,0:36:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小說相關的工作在哪裡都能做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.35,0:36:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,總之你回去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.08,0:36:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.43,0:36:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…我切了點西瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.86,0:36:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有事到如今還會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.15,0:36:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再說這叫什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.06,0:36:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,窮追不捨追到這種小地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.51,0:36:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,別人家的事  你就別管了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.19,0:36:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,已經和你沒關係了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.52,0:36:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,駿！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.58,0:36:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才這話…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.82,0:36:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.02,0:36:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,…你蠢到了這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.50,0:37:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.43,0:37:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.92,0:37:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,駿！快去追她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.57,0:37:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.01,0:37:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼還要回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.95,0:37:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.99,0:37:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.24,0:37:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你這種想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.45,0:37:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不就只是把我當做逃避的藉口而已嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.75,0:37:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.79,0:37:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,駿！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.20,0:37:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去世了就再也見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.12,0:37:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.77,0:37:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,行了  你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.94,0:38:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.28,0:38:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.42,0:38:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,放著新娘不管就逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.98,0:38:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,結果居然說喜歡男人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.77,0:38:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.63,0:38:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,老公！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.45,0:38:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在說些什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.31,0:38:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的吧  駿！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.47,0:38:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.68,0:38:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{前}我沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.23,0:38:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{前}…你蠢到了這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.47,0:38:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{前}你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.35,0:38:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{前}別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.17,0:38:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{前}行了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.66,0:38:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.04,0:39:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦  要給你倆拍照了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.67,0:39:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  你倆笑笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.10,0:39:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,表情太僵硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.96,0:39:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,行啦  不也挺可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.45,0:39:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.01,0:39:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿到甜酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.71,0:39:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.97,0:39:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個一起喝  真讓人開心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.69,0:39:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔  阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.97,0:39:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我要當駿的新娘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.11,0:39:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.14,0:39:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了呢  駿
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.36,0:39:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的哦  約好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.96,0:39:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧？駿
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.79,0:39:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.89,0:39:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,和櫻子結婚的話  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.96,0:39:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.65,0:39:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.98,0:39:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人到海裡去…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.10,0:39:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大晚上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.75,0:39:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很危險的！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.29,0:39:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.41,0:39:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我送你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.63,0:40:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明挽留他就好了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.63,0:40:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.41,0:40:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話  駿肯定就會留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.25,0:40:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.64,0:40:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,明明把自己的私心說出來就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.54,0:40:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這一點  櫻子小姐也一樣吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.43,0:40:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.70,0:40:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不喜歡我…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.58,0:40:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想要和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.33,0:40:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,已經說過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.14,0:40:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.77,0:40:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,駿喜歡上了別人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.50,0:40:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,與他在一起的人不再是我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.28,0:40:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.75,0:40:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,做決定的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.42,0:40:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你能這麼想  是因為你正被他所需要著吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.14,0:40:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.03,0:40:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼和我道歉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.07,0:40:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你又懂得什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.89,0:40:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂得的！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.27,0:40:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.54,0:41:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你一樣珍視他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.49,0:41:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所…所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.29,0:41:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.36,0:41:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.23,0:41:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他要是再人渣一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.38,0:41:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,…就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.11,0:41:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候我媽媽常說  一個人來就會被帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.13,0:41:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,被海？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.29,0:41:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  被帶到彼世
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.93,0:41:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是說這話的媽媽已經去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.35,0:41:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有家人過世  是很悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.27,0:41:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我希望駿不要遭受同樣的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.29,0:41:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他能好好回去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.86,0:42:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.07,0:42:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.88,0:42:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.32,0:42:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.49,0:42:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.17,0:42:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Comment: 0,0:42:11.14,0:42:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.47,0:42:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽身上好香
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.57,0:42:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜歡！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.03,0:42:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,實央！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.78,0:42:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不接電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.60,0:42:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.53,0:42:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？我沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.37,0:42:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,放在屋子裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.84,0:42:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那手機還有什麼意義啊笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.94,0:42:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然…然後
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.78,0:42:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻…櫻子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.92,0:42:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我送她回旅館了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.47,0:42:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她住在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.97,0:42:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她說你今天別去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.19,0:43:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.45,0:43:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,牽連你累壞了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.99,0:43:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？還好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.42,0:43:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,說的是啊  能說得出那種話真是人渣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.28,0:43:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對女生可是要溫柔才行
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.51,0:43:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,都是大人了怎麼還這麼不像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.53,0:43:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.33,0:43:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你慌了？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.04,0:43:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.79,0:43:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.22,0:43:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.85,0:43:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我對你情意已盡
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.09,0:43:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.31,0:43:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就此別過  祝你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.13,0:43:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我已是局外人了  叨擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.10,0:43:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.85,0:43:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.85,0:43:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.87,0:43:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多少回去一次  你的父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.93,0:43:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的  我讀過信了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.34,0:43:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.37,0:43:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  駿
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.80,0:44:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能吻我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.04,0:44:04.88,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,渡輪馬上就要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.17,0:44:06.02,Default,,1000,0,0,,蛤？你在說什…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.34,0:44:07.13,Default,,0,500,0,,這樣我就能徹底死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.51,0:44:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.79,0:44:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,迄今為止你可一次都沒吻過我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.44,0:44:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.25,0:44:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{前}駿他床上功夫很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.35,0:44:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{前}有禮貌又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.14,0:44:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻子
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.19,0:44:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是想和你接吻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.34,0:44:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.91,0:44:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他可以  我也接受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.58,0:44:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再見啦  櫻子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.69,0:44:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.57,0:45:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.98,0:45:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…跟暴風雨似的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.51,0:45:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.05,0:45:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,回家睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.83,0:45:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.71,0:45:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.29,0:45:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好…痛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.30,0:45:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,為…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.74,0:45:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有果斷拒絕啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.51,0:45:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我沒阻止的話
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.24,0:45:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你會就那麼親上了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.13,0:45:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？什麼？欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.29,0:45:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不理你了  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.89,0:45:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  實央
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.64,0:45:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.98,0:45:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.31,0:45:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.49,0:45:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.78,0:45:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,實央說他等會再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.45,0:45:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  你倆吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.16,0:46:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那  等會你倆一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.40,0:46:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.16,0:46:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.63,0:46:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.00,0:46:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.38,0:46:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  還在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.88,0:46:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.89,0:46:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼愛哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.61,0:46:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.22,0:46:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了別…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.81,0:46:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我都已經有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.70,0:46:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,又怎麼會答應那種要求
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.19,0:46:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.98,0:46:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.09,0:46:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把衣服脫了  我想脫！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.89,0:47:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.66,0:47:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你…真的想做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.40,0:47:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊！為什麼不？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.98,0:47:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.39,0:47:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不覺得噁心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.05,0:47:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,才不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.11,0:47:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今還說什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.14,0:47:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你也給我脫了！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.64,0:47:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,實央  你可以當進入的那方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.01,0:47:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的啦  我完全堅持不住…{堅持不住很快射出來，帶兩層套套降低敏感度}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.90,0:47:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才也射過了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.92,0:47:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再套上兩層的話就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.35,0:47:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了不行的…你來比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.55,0:47:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想被進入的一方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.50,0:48:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才去洗了澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.38,0:48:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還做了各式各樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.34,0:48:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,各式各樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.24,0:48:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,行啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.92,0:48:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.51,0:48:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,手指…要進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.64,0:48:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.66,0:48:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己弄過那裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.82,0:48:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事好好告訴我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.99,0:48:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我會來幫你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.91,0:48:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事別管了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.50,0:48:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,進來吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.24,0:48:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.70,0:48:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感…感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.95,0:48:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有點難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.64,0:49:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.37,0:49:03.92,Default,fade,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}能和喜歡的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.25,0:49:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.80,0:49:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.57,0:49:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,別管了…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.90,0:49:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}緊緊互擁在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.59,0:49:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}這種事  我曾以為絕不會成真
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.21,0:49:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.69,0:49:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.60,0:49:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.54,0:49:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.52,0:49:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.84,0:49:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,天婦羅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.18,0:49:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.34,0:49:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.58,0:49:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.30,0:49:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.07,0:49:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼也沒做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.55,0:49:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？做了啊  「各式各樣的」
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.78,0:50:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是說那個啊  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.63,0:50:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我遠比你想像中的更喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.78,0:50:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想要為你做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.06,0:50:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那把這個吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.81,0:50:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了不是這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.18,0:50:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經為我做了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.23,0:50:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是喜歡女生的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.75,0:50:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但即便如此  我還是喜歡上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.47,0:50:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡男生沒什麼值得大驚小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.11,0:50:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說  實央
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.03,0:50:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.44,0:50:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.54,0:51:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.16,0:51:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾得真徹底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.69,0:51:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  收拾著收拾著就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.77,0:51:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思這麼突然要走
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.29,0:51:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.72,0:51:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好好去盡孝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.94,0:51:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,需要什麼就和我說
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.37,0:51:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.61,0:51:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.94,0:51:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.19,0:51:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在看些什麼呢{前文}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.74,0:51:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你這真讓人噁心{前文}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.73,0:51:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.65,0:51:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  北海道肯定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.90,0:51:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.07,0:51:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,記得給我寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.33,0:51:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊不過現在都有手機…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.38,0:51:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.50,0:51:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.33,0:51:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.00,0:51:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.48,0:52:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你獨自在這裡等我  就像我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.95,0:52:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,…不該是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.87,0:52:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,實央！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.31,0:52:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.07,0:52:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起去吧  實央！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.42,0:52:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.63,0:52:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.71,0:52:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要…孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.89,0:52:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,別哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.16,0:52:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.46,0:52:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  駿
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.22,0:52:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,去海裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.84,0:52:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.30,0:52:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.23,0:52:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.47,0:52:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.96,0:52:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好涼！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.94,0:52:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.06,0:52:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,駿
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.85,0:52:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.26,0:52:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我好開心！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.34,0:52:59.40,Default - Top,,0,600,0,,你什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.76,0:52:59.97,Default - Top,,600,0,0,,就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.46,0:53:01.34,Default - Top,,0,600,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.11,0:53:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.75,0:53:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸和媽媽要保重
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.27,0:53:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,接住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.78,0:53:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.09,0:53:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.38,0:53:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.62,0:53:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.97,0:53:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.89,0:54:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,駿  實央
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.46,0:54:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,船要開了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.58,0:54:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.53,0:54:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,實央
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.29,0:54:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
